_item_assets/steam/apps/1677110/extras/03f02d47525da5797319462e825760e4.poster.avif?t=1772726470\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677110/extras/03f02d47525da5797319462e825760e4.webm?t=1772726470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677110/extras/03f02d47525da5797319462e825760e4.mp4?t=1772726470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create the exofarm of your dreams! Make your mark on the world as you build your homestead piece by piece into a handcrafted retro-futuristic farm. Make your place your own with alternative color palettes and decorations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677110/extras/ccc3b965677294432d6914e2a900dbea.webp?t=1772726470\" width=616 height=51 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677110/extras/3acfd6cca39ffabf5933ba1491814a17.poster.avif?t=1772726470\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677110/extras/3acfd6cca39ffabf5933ba1491814a17.webm?t=1772726470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677110/extras/3acfd6cca39ffabf5933ba1491814a17.mp4?t=1772726470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Send resources to remote colonies, befriend interplanetary neighbors, and build a stable of alien livestock. Use the bounty of your harvest to benefit those around you and create a better tomorrow.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677110/extras/13e5619790b19ad53f01966485b364